## ðŸ“Œ 3. Composite Signals & Bandwidth

- Non-sinusoidal signals are a mix of sine waves â†’ Fourier analysis
- **Bandwidth (Hz)** = Range of frequencies \( f_{\text{high}} - f_{\text{low}} \)

